OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780942271
OL,3,CDonohoe inquest expert defends
OL,4,Cobjectivity as firm earned over
OL,5,C#100,000 from DfI
OL,7,FAn expert witness has defended their
OL,8,Fobjectivity at the inquest into the
OL,9,Fdeath of Noah Donohoe as it emerged
OL,10,Fhis past firm has made more than
OL,11,F#100,000 from Stormont's Department
OL,12,Ffor Infrastructure (DfI).
OL,14,FEngineer and hydrologist Jeremy Benn
OL,15,Fgave evidence at Belfast Coroner's
OL,16,FCourt about a culvert where the 14-
OL,17,Fyear-old boy is believed to have
OL,18,Fentered the storm drain tunnel where
OL,19,Fhe was later found dead.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780942271
OL,3,CDonohoe inquest expert defends
OL,4,Cobjectivity as firm earned over
OL,5,C#100,000 from DfI
OL,7,FThe inquest, which is being heard with
OL,8,Fa jury, is now in its 19th week.
OL,10,FNoah had set off on his bicycle from
OL,11,Fhis home in south Belfast on the
OL,12,Fevening of Sunday June 21 2020
OL,13,Fplanning to meet two friends in the
OL,14,FCavehill area in the north of the city.
OL,16,FHowever, he was later seen on CCTV
OL,17,Ffootage cycling along York Road. The
OL,18,Flast sighting of him was on Northwood
OL,19,FDrive.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780942271
OL,3,CDonohoe inquest expert defends
OL,4,Cobjectivity as firm earned over
OL,5,C#100,000 from DfI
OL,7,FPolice believe Noah entered the nearby
OL,8,FPremier Drive stream culvert.
OL,10,FHis naked body was found around 600m
OL,11,Ffurther down the storm drain tunnel at
OL,12,Fa Northern Ireland Railways depot
OL,13,Falmost a week later on June 27.
OL,15,FA post-mortem examination found the
OL,16,Fcause of death was likely to be
OL,17,Fdrowning.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780942271
OL,3,CDonohoe inquest expert defends
OL,4,Cobjectivity as firm earned over
OL,5,C#100,000 from DfI
OL,7,FOn Monday Mr Benn, who is being
OL,8,Finstructed by the DfI as an expert
OL,9,Fwitness, returned for the third time
OL,10,Fto the inquest to continue his
OL,11,Fevidence.
OL,13,FPreviously Brenda Campbell KC,
OL,14,Frepresenting Noah's mother Fiona
OL,15,FDonohoe, put to Mr Benn that he and
OL,16,Fthe company he currently works for,
OL,17,Fand was previously a director of, JBA
OL,18,FConsulting, had a long history of
OL,19,Fworking with the department.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780942271
OL,3,CDonohoe inquest expert defends
OL,4,Cobjectivity as firm earned over
OL,5,C#100,000 from DfI
OL,7,FDfI barrister Neasa Murnaghan KC
OL,8,Fraised declarations at the end of Mr
OL,9,FBenn's statements in relation to his
OL,10,Fobjectivity and obligations in giving
OL,11,Fevidence to the inquest.
OL,13,FHe told the court his statements have
OL,14,F"to be my evidence in place with my
OL,15,Findependent view, not influenced by
OL,16,FDfI or others being a client of JBA,
OL,17,Fand I'm here to assist the court in
OL,18,Fcoming to its conclusions".
OL,26,@vD@AOUzD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780942271
OL,3,CDonohoe inquest expert defends
OL,4,Cobjectivity as firm earned over
OL,5,C#100,000 from DfI
OL,7,FThe inquest heard that JBA Group
OL,8,Fcomprises 10 businesses and employs
OL,9,Fjust over 1,000 staff, with an annual
OL,10,Fglobal turnover of #80-90 million.
OL,12,FMr Benn stepped down as executive
OL,13,Fchair of the company three months ago.
OL,15,FMs Murnaghan asked Mr Benn about a
OL,16,Fdocument showing how much JBA
OL,17,FConsulting has made from the DfI.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780942271
OL,3,CDonohoe inquest expert defends
OL,4,Cobjectivity as firm earned over
OL,5,C#100,000 from DfI
OL,7,FThe company has received over #120,000
OL,8,Ffrom DfI contracts since 2016, the
OL,9,Flargest amount in a single year was in
OL,10,F2025/26 of #47,214.
OL,12,FMr Benn agreed with Ms Murnaghan's
OL,13,Fcharacterisation of the figures as
OL,14,F"not large" and said that income
OL,15,Fwouldn't impact his ability to give
OL,16,Fevidence objectively in relation to
OL,17,Fthe culvert.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780942271
OL,3,CDonohoe inquest expert defends
OL,4,Cobjectivity as firm earned over
OL,5,C#100,000 from DfI
OL,7,F"As a consultancy business we have to
OL,8,Fgive advice to a wide range of
OL,9,Fbusinesses," he said, adding that it's
OL,10,F"very important when giving technical,
OL,11,Ffact-based advice that there's no
OL,12,Freason why you can't work for clients".
OL,14,FMr Benn was involved with drafting
OL,15,Fguidance on culverts in 2010 and 2019,
OL,16,Fand trained staff at the DfI on that
OL,17,Fguidance.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@LO]rD@AOUtD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780942271
OL,3,CDonohoe inquest expert defends
OL,4,Cobjectivity as firm earned over
OL,5,C#100,000 from DfI
OL,7,FHe was questioned about the designing
OL,8,Fof culverts, as he previously told the
OL,9,Finquest the culvert "wasn't high risk"
OL,10,Fbecause of hazards being unlikely,
OL,11,Fterming it instead as "medium risk".
OL,13,FOn Monday Mr Benn agreed that the
OL,14,Fdesigners of screens for culverts need
OL,15,Fto take into account what is
OL,16,F"reasonably foreseeable" and that it
OL,17,Fwas reasonably foreseeable that
OL,18,Fsomeone would be likely to access the
OL,19,Farea around the culvert.
OL,26,@qD@UOUqD@fO]sD@WOUsD@cO]xD@AOUxD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780942271
OL,3,CDonohoe inquest expert defends
OL,4,Cobjectivity as firm earned over
OL,5,C#100,000 from DfI
OL,7,FThe jury was shown pictures of the
OL,8,Fculvert entrance covered by metal bars
OL,9,Fand the inlet area leading down to it,
OL,10,Fwith concrete steps leading to the
OL,11,Fentrance.
OL,13,FMr Benn said the inlet structure "has
OL,14,Fa different set of hazards" to the
OL,15,Fculvert because it is "not a confined
OL,16,Fspace".
OL,26,@uD@bOUvD@[O]wD@WOUxD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780942271
OL,3,CDonohoe inquest expert defends
OL,4,Cobjectivity as firm earned over
OL,5,C#100,000 from DfI
OL,7,F"There are hazards you could fall
OL,8,Fthrough the bars, you could bang your
OL,9,Fhead on the steel or the concrete but
OL,10,Fit's a different hazard set to the
OL,11,Fculvert which is a confined space," he
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,FAsked if it was not inevitable a
OL,15,Fperson gaining access to the inlet
OL,16,Fstructure would then enter the
OL,17,Fculvert, he agreed it was not.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
