PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780942271
OL,3,CDonohoe inquest expert defends
OL,4,Cobjectivity as firm earned over
OL,5,C#100,000 from DfI
OL,7,FThe expert also agreed with Ms
OL,8,FMurnaghan's assertion that reasonable
OL,9,Fforeseeability does not apply to "very
OL,10,Fremote or very hypothetical" scenarios.
